  "description": "有理数的概念",
  "author": "",
  "createtime": "",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "title",
      "content": "有理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "A <b>有理数</b> 是一个实数, 也可以用分数来表示 ( <b>a/b</b>). "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "很多日常生活中用到的数字都可以归类为有理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "threeheading",
          "content": "例如:"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": " <b>1.5 是一个有理数</b> 因为 1.5 等于 <b>3/2</b> (可以以分数的形式表示)"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "class": "center",
          "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/rational.svg\" alt=\"有理数\"> "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "下面是另外的例子:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "border": "0",
          "width": "400",
          "align": "center",
          "content": [
            [
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "数字"
              },
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "分数"
              },
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "有理数?"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "5"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "5/1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "是"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1.75"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "7/4"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "是"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": ".001"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1/1000"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "是"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "-0.1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "-1/10"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "是"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "0.111..."
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1/9"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "是"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "&#x221A;2 <br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t(根号 2)"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "?"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "<b class=\"large\">不是 !</b>"
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "根号2的结果不是一个普通的分数! 有很多这样的数字, 他们 <b>不是有理数</b>  它们有另外一个名称： <a href=\"irrational-numbers.html\">无理数</a>. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "一个非常非常有名的 <b>无理数</b> 是<a href=\"pi.html\">Pi (<span class=\"times\">&#x3C0;</span>)</a>:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi-irrational.svg\" alt=\"Rational Number\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    "
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "有理数的定义"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "def",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "align": "center",
          "content": "<i>有理数是一个整数a和一个正整数b的比<b> a/b </b><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    这里 <b>b</b> 和 <b>a</b> 是 <a href=\"whole-numbers.html\">整数</a> 并且 <b>b</b> 不等于零.</i>"

        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "按照这样的定义，我们来看看有理数:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "border": "0",
      "align": "center",
      "content": [
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "&#xA0;<span class=\"large\">a</span>&#xA0;"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "&#xA0;<span class=\"large\">b</span>&#xA0;",
            "style" : "border-top: 1px solid black;"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "这里b不等于零"
    },
    {
      "type": "threeheading",
      "content": "示例: "
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "border": "0",
          "align": "center",
          "content": [
            [
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "a"
              },
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "b"
              },
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "a / b"
              },
              {
                "type": "TH",
                "content": "="
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1/1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "2"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1/2"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "0.5"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "55"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "100"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "55/100"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": " 0.55"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1000"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "1/1000"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "0.001"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "255"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "10"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "255/10"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "25.5"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "7"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "0"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "7/0"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "<b>错误, b不能为零</b>"
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "一定要记住: b不能为零 "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    }
  ]
}